I never particularly liked pool triathlon, and this was no exception. The race was flat and fast. I remember transition being simply biked leaned against the pool wall, and then in the run we had to go through a filed with cows. I remember a guy wearing Team GB kit being quite scared. ::: {.cell} ::: {.cell-output-display} ```{=html}
